  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13_2",
    "text": "1.沧海桑田",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.11157601115760112,
      0.2852437417654809,
      0.22687122268712226,
      0.30434782608695654
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13_3",
    "text": "(1)现象：地球上的海洋和陆地是不断变迁的。 (②)原因：地壳的变动和海平面的升降是主要原因，此外人类的活动也会引起海陆的 变化。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09483960948396095,
      0.3181818181818182,
      0.9446768944676894,
      0.40118577075098816
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13_4",
    "text": "(3)华例：今天的地球之巅珠穆朗玛峰过去曾经是海洋。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1608554160855416,
      0.41106719367588934,
      0.698279869827987,
      0.43412384716732544
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13_5",
    "text": "2.海陆轮配形成的两大学说",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10227801022780102,
      0.4743083003952569,
      0.3812180381218038,
      0.49407114624505927
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13_7",
    "text": "学说名称 学说内皆 ①22年前，地球上各大洲是相互连 大陆漂移 接的一块大陆、周围是一片汪洋。 学说 ②后来，大陆分裂并缓慢漂移分离形 或今天亡大洲、四大洋的分布状况 ①由岂组成的地球表层不是整体 报块构 一块、而是由板快拼合而成。 热导说 ②大报识处在不断由运动之中 ③板块内部比较定，迎缘交界处 比活跃多火山.地展",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09483960948396095,
      0.5019762845849802,
      0.5774058577405857,
      0.8102766798418972
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13_6",
    "text": "主要证据",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.7112970711297071,
      0.5092226613965745,
      0.8135750813575081,
      0.5270092226613966
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13_8",
    "text": "①大陆轮廊的吻合性 ②拼合大陆几种地层的相性 ③拼合大陆几和生物的相以件",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6434216643421664,
      0.5401844532279315,
      0.9232914923291492,
      0.6238471673254282
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13_9",
    "text": "①阿不卑斯山脉，喜马拉雅 山脉的形成",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6415620641562064,
      0.6646903820816864,
      0.9112040911204091,
      0.7167325428194994
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13_10",
    "text": "②乐非大裂谷，红海的形成与变 ③大面洋的扩张.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6415620641562064,
      0.7272727272727273,
      0.9177126917712691,
      0.7799736495388669
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13_11",
    "text": "济意！",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.09298000929800093,
      0.8168642951251647,
      0.1589958158995816,
      0.8353096179183136
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_13_12",
    "text": "①板块构造学说是在大陆漂移学说的基础上发展而成的，是目前最被普 逾接要、相对完善的一个学说。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
